=== Hurewicz homomorphism ===
Functors and natural transformations abound in algebraic topology, with the Hurewicz homomorphisms serving as examples. For any pointed topological space formula_109 and positive integer formula_110 there exists a group homomorphism

: formula_111

from the formula_110-th homotopy group of formula_109 to the formula_110-th homology group of formula_115. Both formula_116 and formula_117 are functors from the category Top* of pointed topological spaces to the category Grp of groups, and formula_118 is a natural transformation from formula_116 to formula_117.

===Determinant===
