to each matrix entry. Similarly, formula_128 restricts to a group homomorphism formula_130, where formula_131 denotes the group of units of formula_121. In fact, formula_133 and formula_134 are functors from the category of commutative rings formula_135 to formula_51. 
The determinant on the group formula_125, denoted by formula_138, is a group homomorphism 

