There are more than 1,500 castles in Dordogne, making it &quot;The Other Chateau Country&quot; including:

*Beynac
*Biron
*Manoir de la Borie-Fricart
*Bourdeilles
*Castelnaud-la-Chapelle
*Chant√©rac
*Chatenet
